(r) one-parent family payment;
(s) deserted wife’s benefit, and deserted wife’s allowance;
(t) carer’s allowance;
(u) disability allowance;
(v) farm assist;
(w) back to work family dividend.

The bonus payment also applies to recipients of domiciliary care allowance during the month of December 2020, subject to a minimum payment of €20.

